{"tid":788391,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發!) 懷疑TVB愛回家抄橋拎左我朋友段o camp經驗黎用 點算好? 有沒得問TVB拎番錢?","createTime":"2018-08-21T12:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T13:43:38.000Z","uid":44748,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"45786c3a4c2fbe51eb53653aa1b3170af11e58e4","tid":788391,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:26:11.000Z","msg":"TVB愛回家用左阿滕代表左阿叔 然後找少少人物姓名 同我朋友段o camp經驗一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係用班青年同D大人老左先想讀書一齊玩o camp經驗一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n我覺得好慘咁可以點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之前都有用到玩o camp拖埋gip去 呢條都係巴打條橋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\npost 左沒幾耐就比人拎左黎轉少少就用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/782472/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/782472/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n以下為之前個post既內容<br />\n是咁的 我朋友讀榮譽學士學位 <br />\nO camp果時見到有唔少阿叔 40歲左右 佢地係話因為競爭大<br />\n所以讀asso 駁上黎 而asso讀得好就可以用GPA上大學 唔洗考DSE <br />\n大叔話由於係新生關係 年齡差距又咁大<br />\n所以想參加o camp黎識番D人做project<br />\n<br />\n咁我朋友係女仔黎 玩Ocamp果時抽中同D阿叔一組<br />\n佢話心裡當然唔想啦 <br />\n但係人地又沒做D咩野 所以好地地就沒得say no<br />\n唔通話佢地係阿叔唔鍾意就唔一組咩<br />\n實比人話歧視啦<br />\n所以咪要同D阿叔一齊玩<br />\n你知啦 玩得game就一定要有身體接觸<br />\n仲要正日面對面 如果阿叔個樣好D仲可以接受到<br />\n佢話D阿叔個樣成個巢皮妹所佬咁 好噁心果隻 仲有好多頭皮 M額同爛牙<br />\n玩game果時又會拖到手仔 搞到佢覺得成個O camp到好似被人折磨咁<br />\n<br />\n最重要就係比佢發現左D阿叔係玩遊戲果時會RJ 仲要塞隻手入去 <br />\n都唔知係唔係R左入面D袋底泥!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n原本想同隔離D人講 但係佢地RR下收手 差D比人誤會左屈佢地 結果講唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家佢覺得好辛苦 但個O camp仲有2日 D阿叔又沒咩野<br />\n所以都唔咁同組爸組媽用呢D原因伸請換組<br />\n想問咁多位高手巴打可以點解決呢D問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"8a8385942ca8965b6c8c200ff580186321bf9e53","tid":788391,"uid":90166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"搵律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cebb08e53078ddd47de12f9d7d94a10cf3d7a9","tid":788391,"uid":71496,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:43:25.000Z","msg":"膠都廢事比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估佢播出街既係幾日前就拍好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7db4f4cd5038f4ffbb842ced781e25bdd062f5","tid":788391,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:45:43.000Z","msg":"4日又劇本又拍好又後期？"},{"pid":"8ba8186c482a7918caa8e3d60902bd4e565e54ae","tid":788391,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5cebb08e53078ddd47de12f9d7d94a10cf3d7a9","tid":788391,"uid":71496,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:43:25.000Z","msg":"膠都廢事比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估佢播出街既係幾日前就拍好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b982d7347660de7c6cc20cdd38c570453000bf8","tid":788391,"uid":55,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:48:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c497ad2e7ce2cababf7e2e6f261ca6802fde8672","tid":788391,"uid":87394,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"把自己想得這麼高"},{"pid":"49095da67ed799a66b683c347508c9f2c317ae51","tid":788391,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b982d7347660de7c6cc20cdd38c570453000bf8","tid":788391,"uid":55,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5e7db4f4cd5038f4ffbb842ced781e25bdd062f5","tid":788391,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:45:43.000Z","msg":"4日又劇本又拍好又後期？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:48:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"rep